** COOKIE MANAGER 1 extension must be properly configured and fired BEFORE this extension, otherwise all users will be considered opted-out and no tracking will fire from TiQ at all.

** Produces utag_data variables with string boolean values to be used in Load Rules on the library level.  Example for a user who has allowed 'statistics' tracking:

      utag_data.allow_required_cookies = &quot;true&quot;;
      utag_data.allow_comfort_cookies = &quot;true&quot;;
      utag_data.allow_statistics_cookies = &quot;false&quot;;
      utag_data.allow_targeting_cookies = &quot;false&quot;;

